Railsgun
=============

That's a static site generator. How to shoot a fly with a cannon - or take a sledgehammer to crack a nut.

A better documentation coming soon..

That's a rushed release.

Features
--------
* hierarchy organized pages
* multilanguage
* pretty urls
* built with Ruby on Rails
* Heroku ready
* Better info coming soon! Promised!
	
To-do
-----
* a lot of documentation
* a lot of tests

Raquirements:
-------------
* Ruby 1.8.7 or 1.9.2
* Rails 3.0.5
* Some gems - check Gemfile

Installation
------------
	run 'git clone https://github.com/cantierecreativo/railsgun.git'
	run 'gem install rails bundler'
	run 'cd railsgun'
	edit config/database.yml according to your configuration
	run 'bundle install'
	run 'rake db:reset'
	run 'rake pages_tree:generate'
	
Usage
-----
* Generate pages tree via db/pages_tree.yml
* Better info coming soon! Promised!
		
